            <div type="edition" subtype="transcription" ana="b1">
                <p xml:lang="heb">תתני<supplied reason="subaudible">ח</supplied> נפ<supplied reason="lost">שה ד</supplied>
               <gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="4"/>
               <lb/>ד<gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="4"/>
                        ני<supplied reason="subaudible">ק</supplied>ד<gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="3"/>
               <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">דמית</supplied>
               <lb/>בשתה יום בירח <supplied reason="subaudible">נ</supplied>
               <supplied reason="lost">י</supplied>
               <supplied reason="subaudible">ס</supplied>ן <supplied reason="lost">בשתה</supplied>
               <lb/>שבעיתה דשבועה דהי<supplied reason="lost">א
                    שנת</supplied>
               <lb/>ארבע וז מה לחרבן בית <supplied reason="lost">מק</supplied>
               <lb break="no"/>דשה <gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="3"/> דיבני
                        ביומינ<supplied reason="lost">ו</supplied>
               <lb/>שנת ת ארבעא מ<supplied reason="subaudible">א</supplied>ה ישב<supplied reason="subaudible">ע</supplied>
               <lb/>וחיה נה שנים חמשין יוהמ<supplied reason="lost">ש</supplied>
               <lb/>צלי על משכבה <gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="3"/>
                    <space unit="character" extent="unknown"/>
               <lb/>וב<supplied reason="subaudible">ש</supplied>ל<supplied reason="subaudible">ו</supplied>ם <gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="2"/> ותה<lb/>שלום על ישראל ש<supplied reason="subaudible">לו</supplied>ם</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>May the so[ul re]st [of ....]<lb/>of ... Nikod[em(os) ? who died]<lb/>on the
                    sixth day of the month Nisan, in the<lb/>seventh [year] of the seven-year cycle
                    which is [the year]<lb/>four hundred and 7 of the destruction of the
                    [Sanct]<lb break="no"/>uary.... May it be rebuilt in our days,<lb/>year {400} four hundred
                    and seven;<lb/>and he lived {55} fifty-five years.<lb/>Pray concerning his
                    resting place ...<lb/>and in peace ? ....<lb/>Peace upon Israel, peace.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" ana="b1">
                <p>Many letters are shown in parantheses in edited transcription for an unclear
                    reason. This includes: Line 1: ḥ, Line 2: q, Line 3: n, s, Line 7: third aleph,
                    ayin Line 8: n,h, Line 10: shin, w, Line 11: l, w</p>
            </div>
